@startuml
title UC15 - Reset Password Screen Flow
start
:User opens "Forgot password";
:Enter email;
:Submit request;
note right
  Phản hồi trung lập dù email tồn tại hay không
  (tránh dò email).
end note
:Show "check your email" message;
:User opens email link with token;
if (Token valid and not expired/used?) then (yes)
  :Enter new password;
  if (Password policy OK?) then (yes)
    :Update password + consume token;
    :Redirect to login;
  else (no)
    :Show password policy error;
  endif
else (no)
  :Show expired/invalid token error;
endif
stop
@enduml
